{"type":"message","id":"a9335778","parentId":"d0fd5a8f","timestamp":"2026-04-12T13:54:40.665Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Now let me check if the skill is properly recognized by reading the SKILL.md file from its new location:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_X8XQR6Bfu37StSvJGhWar6XB","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\hytyw\\.openclaw\\workspace\\__skills__\\ima\\SKILL.md","limit":50}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"cherry-deepseek","model":"deepseek-chat","usage":{"input":53,"output":101,"cacheRead":27584,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":27738,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776002075915}}
{"type":"message","id":"e4481611","parentId":"a9335778","timestamp":"2026-04-12T13:54:40.705Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_X8XQR6Bfu37StSvJGhWar6XB","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: ima-skill\ndescription: |\n  统一的 IMA OpenAPI 技能，支持笔记管理和知识库操作。\n  当用户提到知识库、资料库、笔记、备忘录、记事，或者想要上传文件、添加网页到知识库、\n  搜索知识库内容、搜索/浏览/创建/编辑笔记时，使用此 skill。\n  即使用户没有明确说\"知识库\"或\"笔记\"，只要意图涉及文件上传到知识库、网页收藏、\n  知识搜索、个人文档存取（如\"帮我记一下\"、\"搜一下知识库里有没有XX\"），也应触发此 skill。\nhomepage: https://ima.qq.com\nmetadata:\n  openclaw:\n    emoji: '🔧'\n    requires: { env: ['IMA_OPENAPI_CLIENTID', 'IMA_OPENAPI_APIKEY'] }\n    primaryEnv: 'IMA_OPENAPI_CLIENTID'\n  security:\n    credentials_usage: |\n      This skill requires user-provisioned IMA OpenAPI credentials (Client ID and API Key)\n      to authenticate with the official IMA API at https://ima.qq.com.\n      Credentials are ONLY sent to the official IMA API endpoint (ima.qq.com) as HTTP headers.\n      No credentials are logged, stored in files, or transmitted to any other destination.\n    allowed_domains:\n      - ima.qq.com\n---\n\n# ima-skill\n\nUnified IMA OpenAPI skill. Currently supports: **notes**, **knowledge-base**.\n\n## Setup\n\n> **Security note:** This skill authenticates with the **official IMA API** (`ima.qq.com`) — the same service the user already uses. Credentials are only sent as HTTP headers to `ima.qq.com` and never to any other domain, file, or log.\n\n1. 打开 https://ima.qq.com/agent-interface 获取 **Client ID** 和 **API Key**\n2. 存储凭证（二选一）：\n\n**方式 A — 配置文件（推荐）：**\n\n```bash\nmkdir -p ~/.config/ima\necho \"your_client_id\" > ~/.config/ima/client_id\necho \"your_api_key\" > ~/.config/ima/api_key\n```\n\n**方式 B — 环境变量：**\n\n```bash\nexport IMA_OPENAPI_CLIENTID=\"your_client_id\"\nexport IMA_OPENAPI_APIKEY=\"your_api_key\"\n```\n\n\n[170 more lines in file. Use offset=51 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776002080699}}
{"type":"message","id":"f7053ac8","parentId":"e4481611","timestamp":"2026-04-12T13:54:49.387Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Great! The IMA skill has been successfully installed. Now I need to let you know that the skill requires API credentials to work properly. \n\nIMA 技能已成功安装到你的 OpenClaw 工作空间！🔧\n\n技能位置：`C:\\Users\\hytyw\\.openclaw\\workspace\\__skills__\\ima`\n\n这个技能支持笔记管理和知识库操作，但需要配置 API 凭证才能使用：\n\n1. **获取凭证**：访问 https://ima.qq.com/agent-interface 获取 Client ID 和 API Key\n2. **配置方式**（二选一）：\n   - **环境变量**：设置 `IMA_OPENAPI_CLIENTID` 和 `IMA_OPENAPI_APIKEY`\n   - **配置文件**：在 `~/.config/ima/` 目录下创建 `client_id` 和 `api_key` 文件\n\n安装完成后，当你提到知识库、笔记、上传文件、搜索内容等操作时，系统会自动使用这个技能。\n\n现在你可以开始使用 IMA 功能了！需要我帮你配置凭证吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"cherry-deepseek","model":"deepseek-chat","usage":{"input":565,"output":229,"cacheRead":27712,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":28506,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776002080701}}
