{"type":"message","id":"9dc9b4a2","parentId":"79e2de7d","timestamp":"2026-04-12T14:07:43.578Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"现在我需要创建一个脚本来调用 IMA API。根据技能文档，我需要先加载凭证，然后调用 API。让我创建一个 PowerShell 脚本："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_itKzUOb780uGWQrlCnQiwpcr","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\hytyw\\.openclaw\\workspace\\create-ima-note.ps1","content":"# IMA 笔记创建脚本\n# 根据 ima-skill 文档编写\n\nWrite-Host \"=== IMA 笔记创建测试 ===\"\nWrite-Host \"\"\n\n# 1. 加载 IMA 凭证\n$clientIdPath = \"C:\\Users\\hytyw\\.config\\ima\\client_id\"\n$apiKeyPath = \"C:\\Users\\hytyw\\.config\\ima\\api_key\"\n\nif (-not (Test-Path $clientIdPath)) {\n    Write-Host \"❌ IMA Client ID 文件不存在: $clientIdPath\"\n    exit 1\n}\n\nif (-not (Test-Path $apiKeyPath)) {\n    Write-Host \"❌ IMA API Key 文件不存在: $apiKeyPath\"\n    exit 1\n}\n\n$IMA_CLIENT_ID = Get-Content $clientIdPath -Raw\n$IMA_API_KEY = Get-Content $apiKeyPath -Raw\n\n# 去除换行符\n$IMA_CLIENT_ID = $IMA_CLIENT_ID.Trim()\n$IMA_API_KEY = $IMA_API_KEY.Trim()\n\nWrite-Host \"✅ 凭证加载成功\"\nWrite-Host \"   Client ID: $($IMA_CLIENT_ID.Substring(0, 8))...\"\nWrite-Host \"   API Key: $($IMA_API_KEY.Substring(0, 10))...\"\nWrite-Host \"\"\n\n# 2. 准备笔记内容\n$noteContent = @\"\n# OpenClaw IMA 技能配置完成总结\n\n## 配置时间\n2026年4月12日 22:06 GMT+8\n\n## 1. IMA 技能安装\n- ✅ 技能已下载并安装到工作空间：`C:\\Users\\hytyw\\.openclaw\\workspace\\__skills__\\ima`\n- ✅ 技能包含两个模块：`notes`（笔记管理）和 `knowledge-base`（知识库管理）\n\n## 2. IMA API 凭证配置\n- ✅ Client ID: `e49eed7e89020c8baec3358d9e9732a5`（已保存到 `C:\\Users\\hytyw\\.config\\ima\\client_id`）\n- ✅ API Key: `xeLf6p2d85BSJnMuYfrFUbQmPT08tUKVEe/fZGsvA5LLVrUKy13zuh3XSWkCnW3CXKKUqG473w==`（已保存到 `C:\\Users\\hytyw\\.config\\ima\\api_key`）\n\n## 3. finops-expert agent 配置\n- ✅ IMA 技能已绑定到 finops-expert：在 `openclaw.json` 中配置了 `\"skills\": [\"ima\"]`\n- ✅ 技能已复制到 finops-expert 工作空间：`C:\\Users\\hytyw\\.openclaw\\workspace-finops\\__skills__\\ima`\n- ✅ agent 目录已创建：`C:\\Users\\hytyw\\.openclaw\\agents\\finops-expert\\agent`\n\n## 4. 飞书频道绑定配置\n- ✅ 飞书频道已配置为仅允许 finops-expert 访问：`\"allowFrom\": [\"finops-expert\"]`\n- ✅ 私聊策略：`\"dmPolicy\": \"allowlist\"`\n- ✅ 群聊策略：`\"groupPolicy\": \"allowlist\"`\n- ✅ 群聊允许列表：`\"groupAllowFrom\": [\"finops-expert\"]`\n\n## 5. 网关重启\n- ✅ 配置已应用并自动重启网关\n- ✅ 网关运行正常，监听端口 18790\n\n## 使用说明：\n1. **IMA 技能使用**：当 finops-expert 处理笔记、知识库、文件上传等任务时，会自动调用 IMA 技能\n2. **飞书频道**：finops-expert 现在可以通过飞书频道与用户交互\n3. **凭证安全**：IMA API 凭证仅发送到官方 IMA API 端点 (`ima.qq.com`)，不会存储或传输到其他位置\n\n## 配置状态\n配置已完成，finops-expert 现在可以：\n- 使用 IMA 技能管理笔记和知识库\n- 通过飞书频道与用户通信\n- 处理财务运营相关的文档和知识管理任务\n\n---\n*此笔记由 OpenClaw 自动创建于配置测试过程中*\n\"@\n\nWrite-Host \"✅ 笔记内容准备完成\"\nWrite-Host \"   标题: OpenClaw IMA 配置总结\"\nWrite-Host \"   内容长度: $($noteContent.Length) 字符\"\nWrite-Host \"\"\n\n# 3. 检测 PowerShell 版本（重要！根据技能文档要求）\nif ($PSVersionTable.PSVersion.Major -le 5) {\n    Write-Host \"⚠️ 检测到 PowerShell 5.1，将使用 UTF-8 字节数组模式发送请求\"\n    $useUtf8Bytes = $true\n} else {\n    Write-Host \"✅ PowerShell 7+，默认 UTF-8，无需额外处理\"\n    $useUtf8Bytes = $false\n}\n\n# 4. 构建请求体\n$body = @{\n    title = \"OpenClaw IMA 配置总结\"\n    content = $noteContent\n    content_format = 1  # 固定值 1，表示文本格式\n} | ConvertTo-Json -Depth 10 -Compress\n\nWrite-Host \"✅ 请求体构建完成\"\nWrite-Host \"\"\n\n# 5. 设置请求头\n$headers = @{\n    \"ima-openapi-clientid\" = $IMA_CLIENT_ID\n    \"ima-openapi-apikey\" = $IMA_API_KEY\n    \"Content-Type\" = \"application/json\"\n}\n\n# 6. 发送请求\n$url = \"https://ima.qq.com/openapi/note/v1/import_doc\"\n\nWrite-Host \"📤 发送请求到 IMA API...\"\nWrite-Host \"   URL: $url\"\nWrite-Host \"\"\n\ntry {\n    if ($useUtf8Bytes) {\n        # PowerShell 5.1：必须转为 UTF-8 字节数组\n        $utf8Bytes = [System.Text.Encoding]::UTF8.GetBytes($body)\n        $response = Invoke-RestMethod -Uri $url -Method Post -Body $utf8Bytes -ContentType \"application/json; charset=utf-8\" -Headers $headers\n    } else {\n        # PowerShell 7+：可直接传字符串\n        $response = Invoke-RestMethod -Uri $url -Method Post -Body $body -ContentType \"application/json; charset=utf-8\" -Headers $headers\n    }\n    \n    Write-Host \"✅ 请求成功！\"\n    Write-Host \"\"\n    \n    # 显示响应\n    $responseJson = $response | ConvertTo-Json -Depth 5\n    Write-Host \"响应内容:\"\n    Write-Host $responseJson\n    \n    # 检查响应状态\n    if ($response.ret -eq 0) {\n        Write-Host \"\"\n        Write-Host \"🎉 笔记创建成功！\"\n        Write-Host \"   笔记 ID: $($response.data.doc_id)\"\n        Write-Host \"   标题: $($response.data.title)\"\n    } else {\n        Write-Host \"\"\n        Write-Host \"❌ API 返回错误: $($response.msg) (错误码: $($response.ret))\"\n    }\n    \n} catch {\n    Write-Host \"❌ 请求失败: $($_.Exception.Message)\"\n    Write-Host \"   错误详情: $($_.ErrorDetails.Message)\"\n}\n\nWrite-Host \"\"\nWrite-Host \"=== 测试完成 ===\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"cherry-deepseek","model":"deepseek-chat","usage":{"input":53,"output":1762,"cacheRead":44800,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":46615,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776002804341}}
